Build Attacker Profile and Select Campaign Objectives
Lab Objectives
By the end of this lab, students will be able to:

Build comprehensive threat actor profiles using MITRE ATT&CK framework
Analyze threat intelligence reports to extract TTPs (Tactics, Techniques, and Procedures)
Define strategic campaign objectives based on threat actor analysis
Create structured documentation for red team operations
Automate profile analysis using Python scripting
Prerequisites
Basic understanding of cybersecurity concepts
Familiarity with Linux command line
Basic knowledge of MITRE ATT&CK framework
Python programming fundamentals
Understanding of threat intelligence concepts
